column1: Adding the litterfall production in the plateau forest
to the annual stand mass increment (6.4 tDWha 1
including 0.9 tDWha 1 of damaged trees) measured by
Chambers et al. (2001) from a nearby plot
NPP of the forest would reach 15.3 t DWha 1 yr 1 which is equivalent to 7.7 tCha 1 yr 1."
